summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of Forty-six and 18/100 Dollars ($46.18), from Local Improvement District No. 1892 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said District, for the improvement of West Seventy-third Street, and other streets, and avenues, all in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, under Ordinance No. 19560.
